          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='28667' id='24' type-v2='text' w='49875' x='50000' y='71083'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='16' underline='true'>Executive Summary:</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='12'>• Fraud is concentrated around specific trannsaction amounts.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='12'>• Fraud rate increases substantially for higher  value transactions however the majority of fraud cases take place in lower value ranges.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='12'>• Transaction volume is highest below $100 and this explains why most of the fraud occurs here too.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='12'>• Fraud does not occur linearly it occurs in sharp spikes over time, indicating more high risk times in the day.</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='5' />
              <format attr='padding' value='5' />
              <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
            </zone-style>
